title: Solar Panel Branch Trimming, Ingrid, Level 4
description: Solar panels in Ingrid have become shaded during summer due to grow of branches above them.  This is only a problem near solstice due to the high solar position.  Peter & Collin trimmed and cut a several branches to provide full sunlight during the afternoon. Result is a sharp increase in midday to afternoon voltage.   incident report migrated from SensorDB.

external_refs.identifier: Passed sanity check; see incident report IR_132
